<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.9.3">
<l>ceyyē ṟīviṉai yeṉṟaruḷ ceyyumeṉ</l>
<l>kaiyār cakkarak kaṇṇa pirāṉē</l>
<l>yaiyār kaṇṭa maṭaikkilu niṉkaḻa</l>
<l>leyyā tētta varuḷicce yeṉakkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He graces me with saying “don’t do evil deeds”,</l>
<l>the lord Kṛṣṇa with a discus that fills [his] hand.</l>
<l>Even if I get a throat full of phlegm, without reaching</l>
<l>your ankleted [feet], graciously make me praise [you].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
